<description>&lt;b&gt;Resistors, Capacitors, Inductors&lt;/b&gt;&lt;p&gt;
Based on the previous libraries:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;r.lbr
&lt;li&gt;cap.lbr 
